{"3588140": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Tune in to the show Part 2", "steam_appid": 3588140, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Tune in to the show Part 2</i></strong> follows the story of <strong><i>Tune in to the show</i></strong>. It features the second half of the show and continues the protagonist's romantic and lewd adventures in the bizarre house. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3588140/extras/da9f53b94ded1b9dec5ca53cc07ae8bf.poster.avif?t=1776772847\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3588140/extras/da9f53b94ded1b9dec5ca53cc07ae8bf.webm?t=1776772847\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3588140/extras/da9f53b94ded1b9dec5ca53cc07ae8bf.mp4?t=1776772847\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> It's heavily recommended that you play the original first to understand the story and the characters. The game features choices that both change the dialogue and let you choose which characters to romance (and have sex with). This is a harem story by default, but you can reject any love interests that you aren't interested in.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3588140/extras/158f5c8b862777d3f557481520293368.poster.avif?t=1776772847\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3588140/extras/158f5c8b862777d3f557481520293368.webm?t=1776772847\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3588140/extras/158f5c8b8